# Identicone ![npm version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/identicone?style=flat-square&logo=npm)

> A random identicon avatar generator Library.

## Public API
```js
(new Identicone).generate(Object options, Function callback);
```
**Parameters** <br/>
_options_: A plain object with uid `{uid: 'your-uid'}` Like email, token, uid etc. <br/>
_callback_: function callback

## Usage
```js
const identicone = new Identicone();
identicone.generate({uid:'example@gmail.com'},
function(canvas, blobURL, dataURL, blob) {
  // document.body.append(canvas);
  // console.log(blobURL, dataURL);
});
```
